@startuml
title 受理闭环 / 可追踪化（DDD-Lite 组件图，当前实现）

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

legend left
[M] 当前闭环必须组件
endlegend

actor "客户端/前端" as Client
actor "运维/开发者" as Ops

package "Interfaces [M]" {
  component "DocumentIngestController [M]\nPOST /documents/upload\nGET /documents/{id}/status" as Controller
}

package "Application [M]" {
  component "AcceptUploadUseCase [M]" as AcceptUC
  component "GetDocumentStatusUseCase [M]" as StatusUC
}

package "Domain [M]" {
  component "Document 聚合 [M]\n(DocumentId, kbId, fileHash, status...)" as DocumentAgg
  component "DocumentRepository Port [M]" as RepoPort
  component "DocumentIdGenerator Port [M]" as IdPort
  component "DocumentSourceStorage Port [M]" as SourceStoragePort
}

package "Infrastructure [M]" {
  component "JdbcDocumentRepository [M]" as JdbcRepo
  component "UuidDocumentIdGenerator [M]" as UuidGen
  component "LocalDocumentSourceStorage [M]" as LocalStorage
}

database "PostgreSQL [M]\n(ingest_documents)" as PG
collections "Local FS [M]\n{root}/{documentId}/{filename}" as FS

Client --> Controller : 上传/查询
Ops --> Controller : 状态排障查询

Controller --> AcceptUC : 受理上传
Controller --> StatusUC : 查询状态
Controller --> SourceStoragePort : 保存源文件（幂等）

AcceptUC --> RepoPort : 幂等查重 + 落库
AcceptUC --> IdPort : 生成 DocumentId
StatusUC --> RepoPort : 按 documentId 查询

RepoPort <|.. JdbcRepo
IdPort <|.. UuidGen
SourceStoragePort <|.. LocalStorage

JdbcRepo --> PG : SQL (SELECT/UPSERT/CAS)
LocalStorage --> FS : 文件写入/读取

note right of AcceptUC
同一 kbId + fileHash 重复上传时
复用既有 documentId，不重复创建记录
end note

note right of Controller
ACCEPTED 是对外响应语义；
UPLOADED 是内部持久化状态。
end note

@enduml
